Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,BARAN'S RAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop your weapon!\NOtherwise, I crush the boy's skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You dirty...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Better hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do, no, if you kill me,\Nwill you really let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in this insect's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What will it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Hyunckel! Forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Between me, who's out of Magic Power\Nand you, it's obvious who can help Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there's someone\Nwho'll be miserable if you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:02:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Her tears are the last thing\NI ever want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, you have to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And go on and make her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make people happy.\NAll I bring is misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to bring misfortune\Nto evil-doers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only reason\NI decided to join your party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'd rather not give Aban another\Nreason to scold me in the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If he hears I abandoned a junior disciple,\Nhe'll reject me for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the attitude! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Larhart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To use a hostage would bring shame\Nto the Dragon Masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And against a human no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you hate humans so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Master Dino, I was born\Nbetween beings of different races.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In my case, it was a Darkling and a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My Darkling father died early,\Nand I was raised by my human mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But, when I was seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,war between Dark Lord Hadorra\Nand the humans began.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just because of my Darkling lineage,\Nthe humans discriminated against me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not just against me,\Nbut against my mother as well!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eventually, my mother fell ill\Nand died a forsaken death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master Baran was the only one\Nwho ever understood my pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You soft fools.\NTo feel my pain as your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met humans like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you will be able to understand\NMaster Baran's pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave Master Baran\Nand Master Dino in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Larhart...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, I have one more request.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you accept my Dark Armour Spear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the armour favors you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have been in battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm glad I met men like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,at the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Larhart, I accept\Nyour will and this armour...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that contains your soul.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like we're doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a plan, Crocodine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If only Hyunckel was here.\NThen we may have had options.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you two can stop me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you have some sort of plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course not.\NThere's no way for us to stop Baran.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only... If only we had one more ally!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that Mage came to stop us\Non the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I left him to the Dragon Masters\Nand came ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:09:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,To sacrifice such a whelp\Nwas unusually cruel of you, Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Or was it the idea of the girl beside you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp... How could he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, you went\Nto stop Baran's forces alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you pretended to abandon us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You chose to be hated. All for Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I actually hit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been such a fool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't realize how determined you were\Nand called you a coward!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me, Popp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can hit me all you like\Nin the afterlife!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your mind, Crocodine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes have been opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran, fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you truly have lost your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, I have a plan. I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous, Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Dragonic Aura!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unbelievable! He blocked an attack\Nimbued with my Dragonic Aura!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran, use your Gigabreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My tough hide is my only strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Only your strongest attack\Ncan take my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall grant your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! My Ultimate Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine seems to be\Nproving quite stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hopefully Baran will be defeated here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I doubt he'll go down easily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Gigabreak!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus ends the Beast King.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Princess!\NNow I can fight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But my Behoma can't heal\Nboth your wound and stamina at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be no stamina to heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the Beast King can survive\Na direct hit with my Gigabreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All I need to do is focus\Nall my power on defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as I'm not a corpse, the Princess\Ncan heal my stamina with her Behoma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit me as much as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My life or your power!\NIt's a contest to see which ends first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A contest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare mock me...\Nmock the power of the Dragon Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you hurt his pride\Nby not dying with one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What an overwhelming Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine, this is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know\Nhow long you'll last fighting like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware that this is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the only way to stop Baran!\NI have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us follow Popp's spirit, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.\NI guess it's punishment for hitting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm burning!\NI can't sit still!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.60,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BLOODY SUKURAIDO!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:03.61,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEAST KING REDEMPTION BLAST{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you immortal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has ever been hit by\Nmy Gigabreak twice and survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Immortality is Hyunckel's thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If I keep getting hit\Nby such an attack, I'm certain I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But if taking my life\Ndrains your power, it's not a bad trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You...! You're not trying to win at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're using your own life\Nto drain my stamina and Magic Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! The mighty Beast King\NCrocodine would sacrifice himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can drain your power, it'll help\Nmy friends who will fight you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends?! No one is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can he trust the humans so much?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that spirit is making him stronger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even with the full power of my Crest,\NI can't crush him like before!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He need a Behoma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A Raiden spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Take another step\Nand become a charred corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with this game of cat and mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I will end it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Larhart's Dark Spear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he interfere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this Lar--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You survived, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But we managed to take out\Nthe Dragon Masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! You speak lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How else can you explain our presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you killed Larhart and took his armour.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Larhart gave me this armour\Nof his own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He died asking me to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave me this armour then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was his dying gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar! Larhart would never\Nopen up to a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran, Larhart told me of your tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How Dai's mother, Soara,\Nwas the princess of Arukido.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And how it was the humans\Nwho took her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your anger\Nand grief all too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But not all humans are evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You yourself know that\Nmore than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For the woman that you loved\Nwas also a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw the most beautiful and most ugly\Nsides of humans at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to handle it, you hoped to erase\Nall of humanity from your sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing that won't erase\Nyour grief from losing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you truly call yourself Dai's father...\NIf you truly love your son...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then shouldn't you reach out to him\Nwith your human heart, Baran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that's what Dai's mother\Nwould want!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran, Hyunckel's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this unnatural pressure\Ncoming from Baran?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I cast it aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This human heart and body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your pandering nonsense\Nwill bring back Soara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To destroy the humans together with Dino\Nis all that drives me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all I live for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I cannot have that,\Nthen I would rather die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Something weird is going on with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will reclaim Dino by force if I must!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I must become\Na Demon Beast to do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,His red blood is turning into\NBlue Blood of Darklings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Report. Heyedras stationed\Nin Teran are disappearing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Extraordinary energy\Nis spreading explosively.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! How can that be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd heard of it, but it seems Baran\Nis taking his ultimate form.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Send all Heyedras in the area\Nto Teran Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran's body...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...Is changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the true form of a Dragon Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The combined power of Dragon,\NDarkling, and human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ultimate Combat Form\Nof the Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That is this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The form known as the Dragonoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baran's power as a Dragonoid\Nis beyond this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.98,0:23:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even Hyunckel and Crocodine together\Nprove to be no match.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At last, Baran finds Dai,\Nwho lost his memories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just when all seems lost,\NPopp thinks of one last plan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.07,0:23:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.58,0:23:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Popp's Resolve"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:23:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
